{
  "stem": "1061.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyhow, in all that, Anna and Irene burst out laughing because they looked absolutely-- well, there is no description, you know?",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Grotesque is the closest, but it doesn't describe.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "These two, tall sticks of women with bald heads-- little-- little heads, you know, starved little faces, bald.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, of course, this was what they call in Polish, 'hangman's humor,' you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This is the type of laughter that really should have been hysterics.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But anyhow, this was the women's section.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we were processed through tattooing, through head-- the head being shaved, whatever being thrown some kind of clothes, whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, if you were a size 10, you got a size 52.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if you were a size 14, you got a size 6, whatever.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, they just threw it at you, and if it didn't fit, too bad.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Wooden shoes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And with-- at the time, when the train was unloaded in Auschwitz, we saw Father emerge from the train.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It so happened that our wagon was adjacent to the men's.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, the men's-- the men's wagons were a few, and they ended.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then the others started.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Where we went in the first female wagon, and Father was in the last men's wagon.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So when we were unloaded, on the platform in Auschwitz, we still saw Father there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But of course later on, he did not survive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very soon, he became very ill because he was-- you see, after Mother-- after Mother was taken away, he changed terribly.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He became totally gray and despondent, and he didn't have that spark in him any more and not a sense of humor.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I think he really lived because we were around.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
